{
  "stem": "7458.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And then we went far away in the forest and we chopped down straight woods and made logs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "We laid those out as a ceiling, about two feet below ground, then except for the opening, where, the tree was going to fit in as a door.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "Then we covered it with earth, about two feet of earth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "Then we covered it with the leaves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And the earth that we dug out we carried on our shoulders, bag by bag, far away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "We spread it in a different part of the forest, so that people wouldn't know where it came from.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And we cleaned it all up so that you could have an army march over the bunker and they wouldn't know that human beings were underneath there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "See, we would come in and then slowly lift that little tree over our head and put it in place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "And when we wanted to get out, we would lift that little tree up, put it aside, and climb out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And that's how we were hiding for a good part of that period in the forest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "Then one day we were discovered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "We had to build another one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "Life was just horrible during this period.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "We did not have facilities for taking a shower or bathing in a stream or anything for practically two years.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "During the summer we could find occasionally a stream where we could wash up, therefore we were full of lice.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "We had no food, practically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "We were starving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "We ate whatever we could catch in the forest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And occasionally, we would go out and beg for food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "I lost most of my teeth during that period.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "They just rotted out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "How we didn't get typhus or whatever, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
